tweet: Hand Hygiene at School! One of the most important steps to keep school staff & students healthy is cleaning hands with soap & water, at least 20 sec. or using alcohol-based hand sanitizer, at least 60% alcohol if soap & water are not available. Info:  https://t.co/OUd5oC7XY6  https://t.co/pi4KZGAOj3
